  "description": "A 32-bit, 5-stage pipelined RISC processor core with Harvard AXI-Lite bus interfaces, configurable single-bit branch prediction, aligned memory enforcement, 16x16 complex multiplier with overflow reporting, CSR/exception support, and interrupt handling.",
